Dorsal abdominal length 1.85, intersegmental suture of abdominal terga I–III indistinct, lengths of abdominal terga I–VIII 0.15, 0.22, 0.19, 0.19, 0.20, 0.23, 0.26, 0.21, tergum VII long, proctiger length 0.14, lengths of abdominal sterna V–VII 0.15, 0.17, 0.16, combined length of abdominal sterna V–VII 0.48. Genitalia: posterior margin of first gonocoxae (gc1) concave, sternum IX (ab9) posterolaterally with a flap-like projection (ab9-lp), posterolateral region of gonoplac (gp) with few setae, first gonapophyses (go1) and second gonapophyses (go2) crenulate laterally, go1 not reaching tip of go2, go2 pointed apically, proctiger (pr) posteriorly with long setae (
